      "date": "2014-05-21 15:45:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nJames, starting to think the test failure is a real problem connected to your patch.  error in test run says \"Failed to provision nodes: Unable to set the number of CPU's for node client-6vm1 error ''.  Your patch touches code related to the cpu table.  This is suspicious.",
